reviewText: I've been a huge fan of Patti Stanger for a few years now so getting this dvd was complimentary to her book, "Becoming Your Own Matchmaker" and the teachings she's relayed on her show, "Millionaire Matchmaker".  This dvd provides a visual perspective to her book, however, if you don't own the book you won't be lost.  What I really enjoyed about the dvd was the special features where you get to see her sitdown with 4 gentlemen who've agreed to participate in a discussion about how they handle the dating scene, moving from dating to an exclusive, committed relationship, sex expectations (when they expect to get it and what happens if & when they don't), all the way to marriage and what makes them want to pop the question...it's all there and from the male perspective.  It was funny and very enlightening.  I've already recommended her book as well as this dvd to several of my single girlfriends. Simply put...watch, learn & enjoy!
Title: Patti Stanger: Married in a Year
